  <brief_title>Outcomes of Intrathecal Analgesia in Colorectal Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Outcomes of Intrathecal Analgesia As Part of an Enhanced Recovery Pathway in Colon and Rectal Surgical Patients</official_title>
