  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Multimodal analgesia, sometimes including intrathecal analgesia (IA), is essential in any
      enhanced recovery pathway (ERP). This study aimed to evaluate the safety, feasibility, and
      optimal IA regimen in colorectal surgical patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
